pull_request.title: BIKE Round 2
pull_request.body:
This PR includes: 

1. Removing BIKE-2/3
2. Removing BIKE-1 Level-5
3. Renaming BIKE-1 Level-1/3 to BIKE-1-CPA
4. Adding BIKE-1 Level-1/3 with FO transformation and with negligible DFR.

pull_request.title: Beginning transition to CMake
pull_request.body:
[This commit](https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/pull/546/commits/c143f40c684f793928419e72a0f8658ce8ef11aa) should have all the major changes so far. 

This is very much a draft and a lot is yet to be done (only FrodoKEM is built right now), but this contains the basic outline of how libOQS (and the tests) will be built.
